data.description: Easily accessible 2-acre horse property in the beautiful Conifer Meadows neighborhood of Conifer, CO! Situated on a lovely, usable lot and conveniently located just 5 minutes from Highway 285 and the Staples Plaza, this no-HOA equestrian property offers the perfect combination of serenity and functionality. Horse amenities include a 2-stall pole barn with an enclosed tack room, water & electricity and loft storage, fully-fenced corral, water trough with heater, lots of extra steel gates/fencing, and access driveway to the rear of the lot. There is a flat pad in the paddock for a round pen. The home itself has GREAT bones and a thoughtful floor plan. With a little TLC and updating, one could really make this spectacular! Upon entering the home, you'll find yourself welcomed into a warm, inviting living space. The layout was carefully planned to allow natural light to flood the interior, thanks to the southeast exposure. Easily enjoy the breathtaking views of the majestic mountains from the sun-drenched living room. The kitchen is a chef's delight with modern appliances and granite counters. It seamlessly flows into the adjoining dining area, making it ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. Retreat to the main floor primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom and access to the back deck. In addition to the main floor primary, this home boasts a secondary primary suite, perfect for multigenerational living or accommodating guests. Two additional guest bedrooms and another full bath provide accommodations for everyone. The 3-car attached garage with workshop offers ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. Lots of available parking for your boat, RV, and toys. This lovely raised ranch home in Conifer Meadows is the epitome of mountain living. Schedule your showing today! VIDEO LINK: https://youtu.be/wRqvR6SwnZE?si=G2_9cdmcyDjtu-0y
